From: Karsten Keil <kkeil@suse.de>
Subject: Fix HFC USB driver
Patch-mainline: 2.6.11-rc2-mm1

The old driver was not fully adapted to new USB ABI.

Signed-off-by: Karsten Keil <kkeil@suse.de>

